{
  "title": "Introduction",
  "descriptions": [
    "The documentation serves as reference for scaling and building the portfolio and to provide a detailed view of the site's visual properties and data models.",

    "The website's structure is based on a simple ideaâ€”",

    "<span class=\"dib mv1 pl2 pv2 bl b--light-gray fw4 dark-gray\">Properties + Data Model = Component</span>",

    "The site uses <a class=\"no-underline bb b--light-gray space-gray dim\" href=\"http://tachyons.io/\" target=\"_blank\">Tachyons</a>, a functional CSS library, to encapsulate related CSS properties into bite-sized classes. The site's visual properties (typography, color, spacing, etc.) are translated into function-based classes to create an immutable, reusable, and scalable visual system.",

    "The site is built with <a class=\"no-underline bb b--light-gray space-gray dim\" href=\"https://middlemanapp.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Middleman</a>, a static site generator, to create dynamic pages and layouts and to automate the website's build process. The website's content is stored in separate <span class=\"roboto-mono\">.json</span> files to create a structured way of locating and editing content and to design data models to generate dynamic visual components."
